description: Deletes a registered passkey, or WebAuthn, authenticator for the currently signed-in user. Authorize this action with a signed-in user's access token. It must include the scope aws.cognito.signin.user.admin.

parameters.name: AccessToken
parameters.description: A valid access token that Amazon Cognito issued to the currently signed-in user. Must include a scope claim for aws.cognito.signin.user.admin.

parameters.name: CredentialId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the passkey that you want to delete.
